接受方除必要的信息登记备案外应将保密信息之原本、复印件或复制本返还披露方，或经披露方书面同意自行将保密信息销毁。</p>\n\n<p><strong><strong>第八条</strong></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong><strong>违约责任</strong></strong></p>\n\n<p>1、接受方因违反本合同而直接导致披露方遭受损失的，应对披露方能够充分且直接证明的损失进行赔偿。</p>\n\n<p>2、接受方之员工、代表人、代理人及外聘顾问违反本合同任一约定时，视为接受方违反本合同。</p>\n\n<p><strong><strong>第九条</strong></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong><strong>争议解决</strong></strong></p>\n\n<p>如甲乙双方就本合同内容或其执行发生任何争议，甲乙双方应进行友好协商；协商不成时，任何一方均可向厦门市湖里区人民法院提起诉讼解决。</p>\n\n<p><strong><strong>第十条</strong></strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong><strong>其他</strong></strong></p>\n\n<p>1、本合同自双方盖章之日起生效。</p>\n\n<p>2、本合同正本一式二份，由甲乙双方各执一份为凭。</p>\n','',NULL,'MIGfMA0GCSqGSIb3DQEBAQUAA4GNADCBiQKBgQCbPpcI9ER/U8YnssdPmDQUQ4sEWf7Jn6bOKWe4\r\nea3JWrmyzdy6Uyl2Wwlpr1OIne1ugDweWRzeS2fPINiMQbEeV/BPe3DrNenRyAsNkx071N5j+PWA\r\n6vQ9gfEcGm6XhhCGMPyONJcsdSLihrVIVKaevcJuKornlaMF6g7CtTDlSQIDAQAB\r\n','MIICdQIBADANBgkqhkiG9w0BAQEFAASCAl8wggJbAgEAAoGBAJs+lwj0RH9Txieyx0+YNBRDiwRZ\r\n/smfps4pZ7h5rclaubLN3LpTKXZbCWmvU4id7W6APB5ZHN5LZ88g2IxBsR5X8E97cOs16dHICw2T\r\nHTvU3mP49YDq9D2B8RwabpeGEIYw/I40lyx1IuKGtUhUpp69wm4qiueVowXqDsK1MOVJAgMBAAEC\r\ngYB3qj5Xy5oFH7ktnpQd2W/DcvD0kL5iAmtcnPPzce+wtvtPRXnwMexS7AeMbHYSZ9G+DKDKr9wd\r\nybgiI+pn6rcwPjFnElcCydm8ZbGA69HW7btjJoA8rcJSYX9GcmhpAqQhL69dav0uEn9CCso0N1c2\r\nBJWB/nF9gWiwSBuSFLoRAQJBAMoK7MEpOr60RL2kLdlA0vrn9iJ4L0RvUfu4rwa/cdGADaRn2j98\r\nGGUP1O3SOS1CVEe26M0s7PGtPVsAw0ubfykCQQDEtDVUDQf73HIwt+6iHYtzObzOjTxBTIg4cx6L\r\nvxphBOesJOf1mXBODfj/Rs4EabtNa6Kdet1Zqbr+bmCgtpkhAkACS/d/BqH1UwVJBpnC03rSgVqJ\r\n78XRyFYtP181+20mzYbaLJgNirKYS4LHJVGjExL0Mb8Zvf3/jVGaPDr8HAtpAkASivJkA/52radO\r\nFGi4e5SDvjOgPQwrE63btG5yugcgkjfMsIX1TwuZMBQC7IfLPrRbbgQcWFK5exiXl4wgWlZBAkAY\r\nKfuELxH9OF5srI4CBHJ5FWlNoQlb78j7E2vv45SK/cqJ9BPTiFGWxrYjUhIz3LOFmf5j0NLqMmP3\r\no6b03PFw\r\n','�_�7���=\"8�;4���\Z>��-��SΩk���R(��Ai}�D�׋!��z]K��_���`#ނ���6ʩ��=oK��Ky}\r0<���=o\\V���� �w�,�<#���Kg�B)�ԃ\0G�',NULL),('32b51eff83c74e66aafbc9d8792d421b','dfasdfsd','adfsdfsd',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'